properties.name: Renee Bloomfield
properties.description: Renee Bloomfield was a 27-year-old transgender woman known to work near Higgins Avenue. She was struck and killed by a car on Highway 8 north of Grassmere Boulevard in 2002. Her death was listed as accidental.

properties.name: Noreen Taylor
properties.description: Noreen Taylor was a 32-year-old woman. She died in the hospital after being found unconscious on Ham Street in the Transcona area of Winnipeg in 2001. Autopsy results showed she died as a result of falling out of or being pushed out of a moving vehicle.
